title.rendered: Alticor Inc Delivers “Birth of a Successful Data Center” Keynote Speech

content.rendered:
Alticor Inc Delivers “eBirth” 7×24 Exchange Keynote Speech.  Todd Temple, Alticor Inc Mission Critical Executive, along with Vantage Data Centers and Fentress Architects, presented a Keynote Speech at the 7×24 Exchange conference held in Orlando, Florida.

The topic was “Birth of a Successful Data Center” and highlighted choosing the optimal project delivery method, decision-making and leading the team to success.  The conference is one of the largest in the country and was attended by over 800 designers, owners and data center professionals.  Alticor Inc Mission Critical Group was also an event sponsor and exhibitor at the 3 day event.
